{"tid":156204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★炒硬！地鐵IT撚又孭大鑊！","createTime":"2017-03-14T14:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T06:33:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf4880f8ddb85ca7450fb4f2cbe11e70e65fc08","tid":156204,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"地鐵售票機bug，廢老輕鬆破解！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名男子去年利用港鐵售票機漏洞騙取超過五萬元，被告承認一項盜竊罪，被判入獄八個月。  53歲報稱無業的被告梁富華，去年八至九月在逾四十個港鐵站利用售票機的漏洞，先放入紙幣再抽出，先後四百幾次用同類手法騙取港鐵超過五萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其後測試涉事型號的售票機，發現如果有人放入紙幣時出現系統錯誤，售票機除了退回紙幣，亦會退回相同面值的硬幣，港鐵其後修復漏洞。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/58c7ecfc6db28cd95c53c82c/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F58c7ecfc6db28cd95c53c82c%2F&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f4d2eafe\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/58c7ecfc6db28cd95c53c82c/</a>"},{"pid":"93fb9eaa7caaf05d675ef051e7260924203004fb","tid":156204,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"53歲無業廢老都hack到，你話呢d IT狗質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17e967ee19b5c37e469d6b0da788c4e7bf70be5","tid":156204,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>53歲無業廢老都hack到，你話呢d IT狗質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524a9c51b45f132449672fb726eb02f959e412db","tid":156204,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"咪好似隔離手機台班垃圾ifandog，一見你話ios有bug，就bl